Background

		Mr. Barry W. Perry serves as a Lead Independent Director of Ashland Global Holdings Inc. and has been its Director since January 25, 2007. Mr. Perry has been an Independent Director of Albemarle Corporation since January 1, 2010. He has been a Director of Arrow Electronics, Inc. since 1999 and has been its Lead Director since May 2011. Mr. Perry serves as a Member of the Board of Directors for Manufacturers Alliance/MAPI Inc. He served as Chief Executive Officer of BASF ... Catalysts LLC since January 2001. He served Chief Executive Officer of Engelhard Corp. of Engelhard Aluminas, Inc. from January 2001 to June 2006 and also served as it's President and Chief Operating Officer from January 1997 to December 2000. Mr. Perry previously held senior executive positions at Rhone-Poulenc and General Electric Co. in the USA. He held various management positions with Englehard Corporation beginning in 1993. He served as a Group Vice President of Rhone-Poulenc from 1991 to 1993. He held a number of executive positions during his 22 years with General Electric Company. He served as the Chairman of Engelhard Corp. of Engelhard Aluminas, Inc., from January 2001 to June 2006. He served as the Chairman of BASF Catalysts LLC since January 2001. He served as a Director of BASF Catalysts LLC since 1997. He served as a Non-executive Director of Cookson Group PLC, U.K. since January 2002 to May 12, 2011. Mr. Perry holds a Bachelor of Science Degree in Plastics Engineering from the University of Massachusetts.Read Full Background




